---
title: HelloHero: Soy-Ginger Chicken & Slaw Bowl with Crispy Shallots & Coriander
description: Sweet chilli and ginger is a pairing that we didn’t see coming but are happy to have in our hearts (and mouth)! It’s the contrast that we’ve fallen in love with and how it goes perfectly with diced chicken as a glaze.

